definitions.definition: On the day after the present day.
At some point in the future ; later on
examples: If you don’t get your life on track today, you’re going to be very sorry tomorrow .

definitions.definition: On next (period of time other than a day, such as a week or a month), following the present (period of time).
On the next day (following some date in the past).

main_definition: On the day after the present day.
secondary_definitions: At some point in the future ; later on
( possibly obsolete ) On next (period of time other than a day, such as a week or a month), following the present (period of time).
( obsolete ) On the next day (following some date in the past).
